mp;w=1536&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></section><section><div class="container | font-heading | py-16 md:py-18"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold | mb-10">Frequently asked questions</h2><div class="py-7 border-b-2 border-b-gray-10"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">1.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Can I use </span><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://Peppertype.ai"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Peppertype.ai</span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> going forward? If yes, then how can I do that?</span></p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="__closeIconClass__f9cQA inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p>The migration of Peppertype.ai would just change the appearance of the platform that you have been using so far. The best part is that the new look gives you an ocean of new things, where you can not only create/generate content but also power your content lifecycle.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="py-7 border-b-2 border-b-gray-10"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">2.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p>What happens to my current plans?</p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p>There are no major changes to your current plan, we are just upgrading the same and providing additional features to heave your experience with us.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="py-7 border-b-2 border-b-gray-10"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">3.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">What if I am not interested in any of the new features?</span></p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p>There are no major changes to your current plan, you can continue using Peppertype.ai like before.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="py-7 border-b-2 border-b-gray-10"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">4.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">I am not happy with the integration, how do I cancel if I am an annual subscriber?</span></p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Kindly reach out to us at </span><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="mailto:support@peppercontent.in"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">support@peppercontent.in</span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> for assistance.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="py-7 border-b-2 border-b-gray-10"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">5.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Does the word count remain the same?</span></p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Yes, the word count remains the same, the good news is Pepper CMP has much more to offer. </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="py-7"><div class="flex gap-x-3 lg:gap-x-14"><span class="text-base lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-90 relative top-2.5">6.</span><div class="accordion __accordion__p8LNf __accordion__zUAe1 font-heading text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold w-full"><div class="accordion__header flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button"><div class="flex gap-2"><span class="max-w-[250px] md:max-w-col-10 accordion__title"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Can I get a demo of the new product?</span></p></span></div><svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block __icon__0_Hmg accordion__icon"><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" fill="#fff"></rect><rect x="0.5" y="0.703" width="46.593" height="46.593" rx="23.297" stroke="#1600E5"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.788 17.06h-1.983v5.949h-5.95v1.982h5.95v5.95h1.983v-5.95h5.949V23.01h-5.95v-5.95z" fill="#1600E5"></path></svg></div><div class="accordion__content" style="max-height:0"><div class="font-body text-base font-normal lg:text-xl | pt-4 max-w-col-8"><p>We are excited to take you through this journey. Click on this <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.peppercontent.io/book-a-demo">link</a> and sign in using your <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://Peppertype.ai">Peppertype.ai</a> credentials and book a demo call with us.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="my-12 mx-6 md:mx-18  font-heading text-white | text-center | font-medium"><div class="bg-purple-60 | rounded-2xl container | py-10 md:py-18"><h2 class="max-w-col-8 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-balance | mx-auto mb-10">Looking to supercharge your content marketing?</h2><div class="font-body font-medium flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center | gap-4"><a class="new-btn-tertiary rounded-full" href="/book-a-demo/">Book a Demo</a></div></div></section></main><footer><section class="container grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-x-8 | px-5 pt-8 pb-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-6 mx-auto"><div><div class="mb-6 lg:mb-8"><h3 class="text-yellow-80 text-small font-medium uppercase  | mb-5">Product</h3><ul class="space-y-2"><li><a class="text-blue-web-90 text-sm | inline-block focus:outline-none focus:text-blue-50 hover:text-blue-50" href="/product/content-marketing-platform/">Content Marketing Platform</a></li><li><a class="text-blue-web-90 text-sm | inline-block focus:outline-none focus:text-blue-50 hover:text