u003c/p\u003e","footnote":null,"image":{"data":{"id":"2282","attributes":{"height":1035,"width":1158,"mime":"image/png","alternativeText":"Group 63578.png","url":"https://pct-strapi-images-bucket-prod.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Group_63578_64ff74305f.png"}}},"videoLink":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cNSu8yemtJo","primaryCta":{"id":"232","title":"Book a demo","href":"/book-a-demo/","target":"self"},"secondaryCta":{"id":"233","title":"Existing User Login","href":"https://business.peppercontent.io/login","target":"blank"}},"featureTitle":"\u003cp\u003eElevate your writing game\u003c/p\u003e","featureList":[{"id":"389","title":"\u003cp\u003eSeamless \u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(100, 49, 196)\"\u003ewriting experience\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","description":"\u003cp\u003eUse your favorite AI assistant with our intelligent text editor, Pepper Docs\u003c/p\u003e","color":"linear-gradient(180deg, #F093FF 0%, #9F95FF 100%)","link":null,"multimedia":{"id":"333","media":{"data":{"id":"2279","attributes":{"url":"https://pct-strapi-images-bucket-prod.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Frame_63224_e90a620688.png","alternativeText":"Frame 63224.png","width":1140,"height":1224}}},"url":null}},{"id":"390","title":"\u003cp\u003eOptimized content, by default\u003c/p\u003e","description":"\u003cp\u003eUse our SEO writing assistant to create SEO friendly content\u003c/p\u003e","color":"linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(181, 170, 255, 1) 0%, rgba(177, 241, 255, 1) 100%)","link":null,"multimedia":{"id":"335","media":{"data":{"id":"2277","attributes":{"url":"https://pct-strapi-images-bucket-prod.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Frame_63229_32867716e5.png","alternativeText":"Frame 63229.png","width":1140,"height":1224}}},"url":null}},{"id":"391","title":"\u003cp\u003eBest-in-class integrations\u003c/p\u003e","description":"\u003cp\u003eWrite error-free with grammar checks, content suggestions and add images to make it interactive\u003c/p\u003e","color":"linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(157, 240, 255, 1) 0%, rgba(253, 160, 195, 1) 100%)","link":null,"multimedia":{"id":"336","media":{"data":{"id":"2280","attributes":{"url":"https://pct-strapi-images-bucket-prod.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Frame_63224_2_508bf1951d.png","alternativeText":"Frame 63224-2.png","width":1140,"height":1224}}},"url":null}},{"id":"392","title":"\u003cp\u003eAutomated audits\u003c/p\u003e","description":"\u003cp\u003eCheck how well your content is written with word count, readability level and plagiarism checks\u003c/p\u003e","color":"linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(251, 181, 209, 1) 0%, rgba(238, 147, 255, 1) 100%)","link":null,"multimedia":{"id":"337","media":{"data":{"id":"2278","attributes":{"url":"https://pct-strapi-images-bucket-prod.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Frame_63224_3_2a7584a3a3.png","alternativeText":"Frame 63224-3.png","width":1140,"height":1224}}},"url":null}}],"footerCTA":{"id":"55","title":"Looking to supercharge your content marketing?","description":null,"primaryCta":{"id":"235","title":"Book a Demo","href":"/book-a-demo","target":"self"},"secondaryCta":null,"list":[]},"faqs":[{"id":"23","question":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eCan I use \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://Peppertype.ai\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003ePeppertype.ai\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003e going forward? If yes, then how can I do that?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003eThe migration of Peppertype.ai would just change the appearance of the platform that you have been using so far. The best part is that the new look gives you an ocean of new things, where you can not only create/generate content but also power your content lifecycle.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"id":"24","question":"\u003cp\u003eWhat happens to my current plans?\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003eThere are no major changes to your current plan, we are just upgrading the same and providing additional features to heave your experience with us.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"id":"26","question":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eWhat if I am not interested in any of the new features?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003eThere are no major changes to your current plan, you can continue using Peppertype.ai like before.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"id":"25","question":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eI am not happy with the integration, how do I cancel if I am an annual subscriber?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eKindly reach out to us at \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"mailto:support@peppercontent.in\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003esupport@peppercontent.in\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003e for assistance.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"id":"28","question":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eDoes the word count remain the same?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eYes, the word count remains the same, the good news is Pepper CMP has much more to offer. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"id":"27","question":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\u003eCan I get a demo of the new product?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer":"\u003cp\u003eWe are excited to take you through this journey. Click on this \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.peppercontent.io/book-a-demo\"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e and sign in using your \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://Peppertype.ai\"\u003ePeppertype.ai\u003c/a\u003e credentials and book a demo call with us.\u003c/p\u003e"}]}},"__N_SSG":true},"page":"/peppertype-ai","query":{},"buildId":"s7Ys-SeWBYyltnQdkKImmpjujco","isFallback":false,"isExperimentalCompile":false,"gsp":true,"scriptLoader":[]}</script></body></html>